data.title: Marines TV
meta_keywords: marine corps combat service support schools
data.meta_description: A brief overview documentary of the modern day training that takes place at Field Medical Training Battalion East, aboard Camp Johnson , NC . This video production educates internal and external audiences on how FMTB-E supports the Marine Corps mission. (U.S. Marine Corps video by Cpl Andrew Kuppers)
